analysis.description:
BWData.addBoostFromTile (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#531-547) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- _tile.claimer == _attacker
	- _tile.claimer == _defender

BWService.storeInitialClaim has external calls inside a loop:
	- isNewTile = bwData.isNewTile(tileId) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#131-133)

BWService.storeInitialClaim has external calls inside a loop:
	- bwData.storeClaim(tileId,_msgSender,valuePerBlockInWei) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#141)

BWService.fortifyClaims has external calls inside a loop:
	- (claimer,blockValue) = bwData.getTileClaimerAndBlockValue(_claimedTileIds[i]) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#156)

Reentrancy in BWService.attackTile (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#194-264):
	External calls:
	- (claimer,blockValue) = bwData.getTileClaimerAndBlockValue(_tileId) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#202-203)
	- (attackBoost,defendBoost) = bwData.calculateBattleBoost(_tileId,_msgSender,claimer) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#213-214)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- seed (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#225)

BWData.addUser (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#441-443) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(user.creationTime == 0) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#442-443)

BWData.hasUser (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#443-446) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- users[_user].creationTime != 0 (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#446)

BWData.addBoostFromTile (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#531-547) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- _tile.claimer == _defender (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#543-547)
	- _tile.claimer == _attacker (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#536-547)
	- require(bool)(_boost.defendBoost + _tile.blockValue >= _tile.blockValue) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#543-544)
	- require(bool)(_boost.attackBoost + _tile.blockValue >= _tile.blockValue) (/unique_chucks/7/0xa935a7d31c680344426bd5d3dc94fb65d1da3c31.sol#536-537)
